Author: piipiistorm
Text: This ain't my first rodeo pardner. Lots of "mindfull" eating, therapy, and eventually forgetting about it. ED who? I dont know that bitch.  Get depressed and spiral out of control  Hit rock bottom. And by that, I mean hit my bathroom floor full impact because I passed out.  Pick myself back up again and start the process all over again. It's what I'm "supposed" to do so I might as well start tomorrow...
